svg.text: Front End Developer and Graphic Designer
UC Berkeley Full Stack Coding Bootcamp
Notre Dame De Namur, Bachelors Degree

Innovative Front End Developer who uses his Graphic Design knowledge as an advantage. Proficient in React, HTML, CSS, and Javascript; plus modern libraries and frameworks. Able to grasp new skills quickly and efficiently, with the passion to learn the process. Patience and detailedness allows me to calmly and efficiently solve problems. Working in teams has always been a treat, where one can bounce ideas from one another to produce the best outcome.

• Work with clients to design their desired project in the timeline and budget they provide.• Develop website and project builder app where potential clients can visit. • Manage firebase database of past and current projects. As well as maintaining host site functions such as SEO and marketing platform.• Research and maintain corporate necessities such as legal affairs, trademarking, and bank statements.

• Create image composites with live models for luxury named items using Adobe Photoshop.• Color correct hundreds of images daily using Adobe Lightroom.• Edit raw images shot from the photo team to have clear white backgrounds and cropped accrodingly .• Check image quality for any immediate issues that would be created from other departments.
